description: Deletes specified tags from an Amazon EKS resource.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource to delete tags from.

parameters.name: tagKeys
parameters.description: The keys of the tags to remove. (string) --- One part of a key-value pair that make up a tag. A key is a general label that acts like a category for more specific tag values.
